《聖母升天》共分三個層次，最低一層是神態動作各不相同的使徒們。中間是著紅袍、藍斗篷的聖母瑪利亚被[[智天使|智天使]]們蜂擁著飛向天堂。頂部是俯視下方的[[上帝|上帝]]，上帝周圍的一個天使拿著聖母的王冠。<ref name="assumptionofmary">{{cite book | title=The Renaissance: A History of Civilization in Italy from the Birth of Petrarch to the Death of Titian - 1204 to 1576 | url=https://archive.org/details/renaissancehisto05dura_0 | last=Durant|first= Will | year=1953 | publisher=Simon and Schuster | location=New York | pages=[https://archive.org/details/renaissancehisto05dura_0/page/778 778] | isbn=0-671-61600-5}}</ref>

